Ext.data.JsonP['Arrow_Builder_0.4.0_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Arrow Builder 0.4.0 - 21 May 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46239590\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Arrow Builder 0.4.0 - 21 May 2015</h1>\n    <p>Initial release.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239590_ArrowBuilder0.4.0ReleaseNote-KnownIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Known Issues</span></h2>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-46239590_ArrowBuilder0.4.0ReleaseNote-ETIMEDOUTisreturnedwhenyoupublishanArrowapp\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>ETIMEDOUT is returned when you publish an Arrow app</span></h3>\n    <p>Occasionally, when publishing an Arrow application, the CLI may return an ETIMEOUT error (<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-654\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-654</a>).  To workaround this issue, try republishing the application again.    </p>\n    </div>\n    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46239590\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Arrow Builder 0.4.0 Release Note"});